reviewText:
You can never go wrong with a Scooby-Doo movie.
My son absolutely loves the movies

The Best Scooby Doo movie I've seen so far.  Fans of Fantasy games will especially love these.  These are some of the more believable & entertaining of the Scooby Doo movies.  I won't say anymore, I don't want to reveal anymore.

The DVDs work great and the case is sturdy.
Also, Abraka-Doo was an amazing watch, highly recommend. ... Goblin King was a turd; not even a mystery. Worth it for Abraka-Doo.
Great quality and fast time arriving :)
Not one of our favorites but it's still Scooby Doo.
